00199     struct set_last_attr {
00200       set_last_attr(ParserState &state_) : state(state_) { }
00201       void operator()(char const *str, char const *end) const {
00202         Attribute attr;
00203         hash_map<String,String>::iterator iter;
00204 
00205         state.attr_map[state.last_attr_name] = state.last_attr_value;
00206         iter = state.attr_map.find(state.last_attr_name);
00207         if(iter == state.attr_map.end())
00208           HT_THROW(Error::HYPERSPACE_CLI_PARSE_ERROR,
00209                    "Error: Problem setting attribute");
00210 
00211         attr.name = (*iter).first.c_str();
00212         attr.value = (*iter).second.c_str();
00213         attr.value_len = strlen((const char*) attr.value);
00214         state.attrs.push_back(attr);
00215         state.last_attr_size = attr.value_len;
00216       }
00217       ParserState &state;
00218     };
